source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT id,[LookupTypeId] as masterlookuptypeid
      ,[Code]
      ,[Description]
      ,9 as [SequenceNumber] 
	  ,Cast('9' as bit) as [IsActive]
      ,[CreatedBy]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[ModifiedBy]
      ,[SysStartTime]
      ,[SysEndTime]
  FROM [ZeusColver].[dbo].[MasterLookup]

select cast(id as int) as id,
	[Type],
    cast('1' as bit) as [IsEditableFromUI] ,
	cast('1' as bit) as [IsActive]
      ,[CreatedBy]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[ModifiedBy]	  from MasterLookupType
select code,name,isdcode,cast('9' as bit) as isactive from Country
select *,cast('9' as bit) as isactive  from state

select a.*,cnt.code as countrycode,st.code as statecode,z.PostalCode as zipcode,c.name as city, 
cn.Name as county , st.Id as stateid, cnt.id as countryid, cast('9' as bit) as isactive 
from address a
inner join zip z on a.ZipId=z.id
inner join City c on z.cityid=c.id
inner join county cn on cn.Id=c.CountyId
inner join state st on st.Id=cn.StateId
inner join Country cnt on cnt.Id=st.CountryId

select 
Name,
StatusStyleId,
CAST('9' AS BIT) as IsManualStatus,
CAST('9' AS BIT) CanBeChangedByPatient,
CAST('9' AS BIT) CanBeChangedByUser,
CAST('9' AS BIT) IsCompleted,
CAST('9' AS BIT) IsActive,
CreatedBy,
CreatedOn,
ModifiedBy,
CAST('9' AS BIT) IsInProgressStatus
from AppointmentStatus

select 
   [Name]
      ,[BackgroundColor]
      ,[IsVisibleOnWebScheduler]
      ,[IsRevenue]
      ,CAST('1' AS BIT) [IsActive]
      ,[CreatedBy]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[ModifiedBy]
   
      ,1 as [SequenceNumber]
      ,CAST('1' AS BIT) [IsNonEyeExamType]
from AppointmentType

SELECT [FirstName]
      ,[MiddleName]
      ,[LastName]
      ,[Email]
      ,[PayrollId]
      ,CAST('1' AS BIT) AS [IsLocked]
      ,[LockedSince]
      ,[LockedBy]
      ,[IsPresaleDiscountAllowed]
      ,[IsAfterSaleDiscountAllowed]
      ,CAST('1' AS BIT) AS [IsActive]
      ,[CreatedBy]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[ModifiedBy]
      ,[SysStartTime]
      ,[SysEndTime]
      ,1 as usertypeid
      ,CAST('1' AS BIT) AS [IsWriteOffAllowed]
  FROM [ZeusColver].[dbo].[User]

SELECT [Code]
      ,[Description]
      ,CAST('1' AS BIT) AS [IsActive]
      ,1 AS [LensReplenishmentGenerateTime]
      ,1 AS [CreatedBy]
      ,GETDATE() AS [CreatedOn]
      ,1 AS [ModifiedBy]
  FROM [ZeusColver].[dbo].[Timezone]

SELECT [Code]
      ,[Description]
      ,[StatusHotLineReceipt]
      ,[ReceiptMessage]
      ,[PaymentLImitId]
      ,[RemoteEdgeLimit]
      ,[CanTraceFrame]
      ,[CanAcceptJob]
      ,[CanOnlyAcceptFinishLens]
      ,[CanAcceptNonFinishLensWithARC]
      ,[MaximumPartialRefundPercentage]
      ,[LensReplenishmentMinCost]
      ,[LensReplenishmentMinQuantity]
	  ,cast('9' as bit) as  [IsActive]
	  ,9 as [CreatedBy]
	  ,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP as [CreatedOn]
	  ,9 as [ModifiedBy]
  FROM [ZeusColver].[dbo].[CompanyCategory]
